the : definite article, singular
treasure : common noun, singular, part of the compound noun "treasure map"
map : common noun, singular, direct object of the verb "hide"

Sentence: When is the next flight to London?
when : interrogative adverb, adjunct indicating time
is : verb "be", present tense, third person singular
the : definite article, singular
